1
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:34,980
=Wonder Wall=

2
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:37,900
=Episode 4=

3
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:51,479
Mr. Yu,

4
00:02:51,959 --> 00:02:52,880
the surveillance footage

5
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:53,080
(Ziyu Property Management)

6
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,880
(Ziyu Property Management)
can't be shown to just anyone.

7
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,759
What if someone

8
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,479
recorded it on their phone

9
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,959
and posted it online?

10
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:02,040
How could we protect

11
00:03:02,079 --> 00:03:03,440
the residents' privacy?

12
00:03:03,639 --> 00:03:05,000
Even if no one recorded it,

13
00:03:05,239 --> 00:03:06,320
it's still not appropriate

14
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,199
for others to see it.

15
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,919
We need to do our best to protect

16
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:09,919
everyone's privacy,

17
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,880
including yours.

18
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,160
Right?

19
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,479
Don't give me that privacy talk.

20
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,639
You can't ensure basic safety,

21
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,479
let alone privacy.

22
00:03:14,679 --> 00:03:16,359
Just show me the footage.

23
00:03:16,519 --> 00:03:17,679
Mr. Yu, how about this?

24
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,160
You call the police right now.

25
00:03:19,239 --> 00:03:20,359
Once they're here,

26
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:21,679
we will show you

27
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,720
whatever you want to see.

28
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,720
Is that okay?

29
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,759
There's nothing to see now.

30
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,079
All three camera wires

31
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:27,919
have been cut off.

32
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,560
When did it happen?

33
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,880
Probably sometime last night.

34
00:03:31,239 --> 00:03:32,160
Qiu was asleep.

35
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,560
The one at this gate,
on the main road,

36
00:03:33,799 --> 00:03:34,720
by rows five and six,

37
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,400
and at the east end,

38
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:36,160
all dead.

39
00:03:36,239 --> 00:03:37,120
How did you carry out

40
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,079
the security job then?

41
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,199
How are we supposed to

42
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,359
live safely here?

43
00:03:40,519 --> 00:03:41,079
We can't even

44
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,040
check the footage now.

45
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,040
You had the nerve to sleep?

46
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:43,840
What were you thinking?

47
00:03:44,359 --> 00:03:44,679
Yes.

48
00:03:44,679 --> 00:03:45,759
Mr. Yu, you're absolutely right.

49
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,560
I'll get someone

50
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,280
on it right away.

51
00:03:48,519 --> 00:03:49,440
We'll get the...

52
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,600
I don't need you to fix it.

53
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,679
I just want to

54
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,199
check yesterday's footage.

55
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,560
Those two knew this place

56
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,519
really well.

57
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,359
They slipped in and out

58
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,280
without any trouble.

59
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,040
They were fast.

60
00:03:58,359 --> 00:03:59,040
How's that possible?

61
00:04:00,519 --> 00:04:01,880
If they're familiar with this place,

62
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,120
could they be someone you know?

63
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,799
He can't afford
the property management fees,

64
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:22,919
and he's so arrogant.

65
00:04:23,119 --> 00:04:24,280
Don't put on airs

66
00:04:24,479 --> 00:04:25,960
just because you own a villa.

67
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,160
If you ask me,

68
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:28,960
that Hong guy...

69
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:30,640
he's the one

70
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,239
who tricked him.

71
00:04:31,559 --> 00:04:32,520
About Unit 505,

72
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,840
Lu mentioned it just the other day.

73
00:04:34,239 --> 00:04:35,280
When he was on duty, he saw something

74
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,119
hanging from the beam,

75
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,720
swinging back and forth.

76
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,799
He shined his flashlight.

77
00:04:38,799 --> 00:04:39,520
There was nothing.

78
00:04:39,679 --> 00:04:40,520
Don't mention it again.

79
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,040
Do you hear me?

80
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,520
It's not exactly

81
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,439
something to brag about.

82
00:04:45,359 --> 00:04:46,319
You and your big mouth.

83
00:04:46,359 --> 00:04:47,280
Yes, Ms. Jiang.

84
00:05:08,239 --> 00:05:08,879
Wipe your hands.

85
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:19,359
Mom,

86
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,559
are you so determined to divorce my dad?

87
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,520
Don't ask nonsense.

88
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:24,960
I know.

89
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,040
It's because of me

90
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,679
that Grandma won't let you
have another baby.

91
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:29,760
At your age,

92
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,200
it's going to be really difficult.

93
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,760
Anyone would feel bad

94
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,640
about that.

95
00:05:33,679 --> 00:05:34,999
How old am I really?

96
00:05:34,999 --> 00:05:35,640
My age?

97
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,559
You're a little kid.

98
00:05:37,239 --> 00:05:37,840
What do you know?

99
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:38,999
You even know about giving birth?

100
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,359
Why wouldn't I?

101
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,520
Look,

102
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,119
it's not a big deal these days.

103
00:05:43,559 --> 00:05:44,600
You want a baby? Then have one.

104
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:45,960
Don't worry about Grandma.

105
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,439
I actually want a sibling.

106
00:05:47,679 --> 00:05:48,319
That would be fun.

107
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,080
You want a sibling?

108
00:05:50,239 --> 00:05:51,439
Someone to play with?

109
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:52,119
To treat like a toy?

110
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:52,640
No.

111
00:05:52,999 --> 00:05:54,239
I'd treat them like treasure.

112
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,559
You treat me like treasure,

113
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,879
so I'd treat them the same way.

114
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:58,919
I'd protect them.

115
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,600
Well, looks like we raised you right.

116
00:06:04,559 --> 00:06:05,840
You've really grown up.

117
00:06:06,679 --> 00:06:07,520
You sound just like

118
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,080
Yufeng now.

119
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,520
Grandma said you take after
whoever raised you.

120
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,600
So I take after you.

121
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:12,960
What else does she tell you?

122
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,239
She said

123
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,919
that you and my dad used to

124
00:06:15,919 --> 00:06:17,080
goof around

125
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,679
all the time.

126
00:06:17,999 --> 00:06:19,239
Like two happy fools.

127
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,720
But it's different now.

128
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:22,559
Neither of you is happy anymore.

129
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,160
If separation can make you happier,

130
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,160
then get divorced.

131
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:29,679
I'll be fine on my own,
like a little lonely weed.

132
00:06:32,799 --> 00:06:34,239
A weed? You can't fool me with that.

133
00:06:36,359 --> 00:06:36,799
Even if

134
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,840
we get divorced,

135
00:06:38,119 --> 00:06:39,319
as long as you still call me mom,

136
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,119
I'll always be your mom.

137
00:06:41,479 --> 00:06:42,200
Okay then.

138
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,080
If I ever start wilting away,

139
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,160
promise you'll water me.

140
00:06:45,359 --> 00:06:46,600
You look down on your dad too much.

141
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,280
Hasn't he been

142
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,080
the one cooking?

143
00:06:48,799 --> 00:06:49,239
Mom,

144
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:50,840
can I have a bite?

145
00:06:52,919 --> 00:06:53,520
Oh, sorry.

146
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:55,439
Here.

147
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,040
Your grandma.

148
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,160
Mom.

149
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,400
Did that old witch

150
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,479
come to take over your shift?

151
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,720
She's not here yet.

152
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,439
When are you coming home?

153
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,879
You were up all night.

154
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:09,919
What do you want to eat?

155
00:07:10,919 --> 00:07:11,879
Wontons, rice noodles,

156
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,919
or noodles with pig ears?

157
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,160
Don't go to all that trouble.

158
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:14,960
I have work later.

159
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:16,999
You're my daughter.

160
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,760
I don't mind being tired.

161
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,879
I'm willing to.

162
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,600
Come back early.

163
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,679
I'll make you something good.

164
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,280
Okay, anything is fine.

165
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:24,919
I'm hanging up.

166
00:07:25,679 --> 00:07:26,119
Okay.

167
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,280
Useless.

168
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,760
Never knew how to be thoughtful.

169
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,160
Such a shame.

170
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:01,510
(Lindao Nursing Home)

171
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,080
Madam, have some more.

172
00:08:03,359 --> 00:08:04,400
Thank you, Nuo.

173
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,080
Thank you.

174
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,479
Thank you. You've worked hard.

175
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:13,999
Would you like another bowl?

176
00:08:14,999 --> 00:08:15,879
Another bowl?

177
00:08:16,999 --> 00:08:17,919
Yes, please. Thank you.

178
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,520
Thank you.

179
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,190
(Mr. Yu)

180
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,360
Would you like some porridge?

181
00:08:39,319 --> 00:08:39,559
Sure.

182
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:43,880
Have some more.

183
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:44,679
Okay, thank you.

184
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:49,190
(Mr. Yu)

185
00:08:52,959 --> 00:08:53,480
Hello, sir.

186
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,040
You're here.

187
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,679
Please come in.

188
00:09:05,439 --> 00:09:06,000
All these years,

189
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:08,480
you haven't come

190
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,439
to see your mother once.

191
00:09:11,079 --> 00:09:12,000
She'll be out soon.

192
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,160
Don't start with me.

193
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:52,919
Stop!

194
00:09:59,280 --> 00:09:59,919
What are you doing here?

195
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,599
He is here for me.

196
00:10:04,079 --> 00:10:04,439
For you?

197
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,040
What do you want from her?

198
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:09,839
Mr. Yu,

199
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,360
I've told you

200
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:12,760
I'm no longer responsible

201
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,799
for that villa's
property management fees.

202
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:14,919
Over 30 calls?

203
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:15,839
You've seriously

204
00:10:15,839 --> 00:10:16,640
disrupted my life.

205
00:10:16,959 --> 00:10:17,640
That's harassment.

206
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,199
I could call the police.

207
00:10:20,839 --> 00:10:21,480
Go ahead.

208
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:23,480
At least that would be upfront.

209
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,760
Don't do those

210
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:25,719
shady things.

211
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,919
What exactly

212
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:27,959
do you want?

213
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,280
I don't get what you mean.

214
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,079
Perhaps you should go back

215
00:10:33,079 --> 00:10:33,520
to check

216
00:10:33,959 --> 00:10:35,040
if you left anything behind?

217
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:35,559
No need.

218
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:36,919
That house has nothing

219
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,679
to do with me anymore.

220
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:38,400
Fine.

221
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,000
It's a deal.

222
00:10:41,079 --> 00:10:41,919
Let's sign a contract.

223
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,959
Sign your name

224
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:44,760
and press your thumb.

225
00:10:46,439 --> 00:10:46,919
Stop!

226
00:10:47,199 --> 00:10:47,919
I'll handle

227
00:10:47,959 --> 00:10:48,959
my own business.

228
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:50,919
Either stay out of it

229
00:10:51,839 --> 00:10:52,919
or find a different way.

230
00:11:00,199 --> 00:11:01,199
The house is yours now.

231
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:02,640
No need to tell me.

232
00:11:32,370 --> 00:11:36,760
(2018)

233
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:26,400
It's New Year.

234
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:29,719
Have a drink with me.

235
00:12:46,079 --> 00:12:46,599
Just one sip.

236
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:01,799
Come on, just one drink.

237
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:05,919
Only when I'm drunk

238
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,120
can I see your dad.

239
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,719
I need to talk to him.

240
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:14,640
Like what?

241
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,480
That you're sorry you blamed him?

242
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:17,880
Or that

243
00:13:18,959 --> 00:13:20,599
he deserved to die protecting you?

244
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,679
Only a fool like Chen Liyang

245
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,599
would hang himself from a beam

246
00:13:30,599 --> 00:13:31,719
for someone like you.

247
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,400
The saddest thing in his life

248
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,079
was marrying you.

249
00:13:42,919 --> 00:13:43,959
He wanted to.

250
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:13,599
Happy New Year.

251
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:57,390
(Luzhou No. 1 Women's Prison)

252
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:12,319
This way.

253
00:15:32,719 --> 00:15:33,599
The lock is open.

254
00:16:27,079 --> 00:16:28,120
Ms. Li, are you okay?

255
00:16:32,919 --> 00:16:33,480
I'm still alive.

256
00:16:36,079 --> 00:16:36,760
She didn't come.

257
00:16:38,280 --> 00:16:38,959
Did she come by?

258
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:47,760
How is she?

259
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:49,880
She is thinner.

260
00:16:51,559 --> 00:16:52,640
She still

261
00:16:53,319 --> 00:16:54,280
won't take anything.

262
00:16:57,559 --> 00:16:58,760
After 22:00,

263
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,240
she'd go to the supermarket

264
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,160
to buy discounted food.

265
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:04,760
She had such a sweet tooth as a kid.

266
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:09,040
Before one performance,
she gained three pounds.

267
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:11,480
She just couldn't lose it
no matter what.

268
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:13,639
People

269
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:17,280
really do change.

270
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,559
She just can't

271
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,639
get past it.

272
00:17:26,639 --> 00:17:27,879
I know that feeling.

273
00:17:31,119 --> 00:17:32,200
No matter how big the problem,

274
00:17:32,559 --> 00:17:33,720
in the end,

275
00:17:34,559 --> 00:17:35,760
time will wash it away.

276
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:38,639
Some things would just linger

277
00:17:39,879 --> 00:17:40,480
for a lifetime.

278
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:46,599
Like you?

279
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,040
Someone with an obsession is innocent.

280
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,359
That's why you

281
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,760
come see me every year on my birthday,

282
00:17:56,359 --> 00:17:57,680
a prisoner

283
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,760
who's worth nothing.

284
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,000
Most of the time,

285
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,799
Zinuo just ignores you,

286
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:09,920
yet you give her everything

287
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:10,720
without holding back.

288
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:14,920
I know

289
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,119
you are Chen Liyang's eyes,

290
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:21,079
watching me for him.

291
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,399
Ms. Li,

292
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,399
Unit 505

293
00:18:40,280 --> 00:18:40,920
has been sold.

294
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:44,599
How did you know?

295
00:18:46,879 --> 00:18:48,879
The buyer went to see Zinuo.

296
00:18:50,119 --> 00:18:50,920
What did he say?

297
00:18:52,040 --> 00:18:53,040
